{
  "stem": "7069.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was an automatic thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The prisoners next them would have to carry them away, putting them on big body piles, who then eventually would be thrown onto some car-- cars, trucks, and would be taken to the crematorium to be burned.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Nothing else happened there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Except I developed something very, very miserable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I developed a-- a growth under my left arm here, that started to grow and grow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and eventually developed into the size of-- of an orange, big orange, grapefruit almost.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so I couldn't put my arm close to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it started, also, to invade my body.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I got-- became feverish and sick feeling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And sometimes I couldn't stand up straight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my brother was with me, who helped me standing on my feet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because it would have been dangerous otherwise.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so he was always with me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "When we were driven back into the barracks he was behind me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because when we were driven in, we were driven in, literally by-- by with beatings, gun butts.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Always hollered, faster, faster, faster, they hollered, and would beat us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And so-- and I couldn't move in between the people who were clamping together in front of a narrow door.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Because I would faint when-- when my arm would be squeezed too hard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so I stood at the end of it, rather taking the beating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But my brother would stand in-- in back of me, and would catch all this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And so eventually, we came into the barracks that way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And suddenly it came out that-- as I say, I was fairly helpless.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "My brother was constantly with me there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
